 eye tracking technicians in the world having conducted over 15,000 field interviews in more than 15 countries. Our depth of knowledge and experience related to eye tracking research enables our dedicated team to provide insights unmatched by other providers.\r\n\r\n[/section]\r\n\r\n[list_team_members]', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '10-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-03-17 21:42:51', '2015-03-17 21:42:51', '', '10', 'http://localhost:8888/10-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `ef_posts` VALUES('59', '1', '2015-03-17 21:48:11', '2015-03-17 21:48:11', 'Scott McEachen has pioneered the practical use of cutting edge technology for quantitative market research in multiple and varied retail environments since 2008. In that time he has also personally conducted over 5,000 eye tracking interviews in 10 countries, many including major neuro-marketing components. Scott holds a BA in Teledramatic Arts and Technology from California State University, Monterey Bay, and remains a devout film nerd, self professed toy &amp; collectibles geek, and travel junkie.', 'Scott McEachen', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'scott-mceachen', '', '', '2015-03-17 21:48:11', '2015-03-17 21:48:11', '', '0', 'http://localhost:8888/?post_type=team_members&#038;p=59', '0', 'team_members', '', '0');
