ut process. Most often, these interruptions occured during the payment stage of checking out with 8% of all respondents encountering some interruption during payment. \n\n\n', 'Checking Out at the Grocery Store', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '178-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-04-07 22:28:20', '2015-04-07 22:28:20', '', '178', 'http://ef.zendentest.com/178-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
